{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CanvasGradient","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.CanvasGradient"],"baseline":{"baseline":"high","baseline_high_date":"2018-01-29","baseline_low_date":"2015-07-29","support":{"chrome":"1","chrome_android":"18","edge":"12","firefox":"1.5","firefox_android":"4","safari":"2","safari_ios":"1"}},"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li class=\"section\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></li><li class=\"section\"><em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>CanvasGradient</code></a></em></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient/addColorStop\"><code>addColorStop()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>OffscreenCanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/createImageBitmap\"><code>Window.createImageBitmap()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/createImageBitmap\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.createImageBitmap()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard note\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<p>The <strong><code>CanvasGradient</code></strong> interface represents an <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opaque_data_type\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">opaque object</a> describing a gradient. It is returned by the methods <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createLinearGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient()</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createConicGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createConicGradient()</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createRadialGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createRadialGradient()</code></a>.</p>\n<p>It can be used as a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillStyle\" title=\"fillStyle\"><code>fillStyle</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeStyle\" title=\"strokeStyle\"><code>strokeStyle</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instance_properties","title":"Instance properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>As an opaque object, there is no exposed property.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instance_methods","title":"Instance methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"canvasgradient.addcolorstop\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient/addColorStop\"><code>CanvasGradient.addColorStop()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Adds a new stop, defined by an <code>offset</code> and a <code>color</code>, to the gradient.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/canvas.html#canvasgradient","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.CanvasGradient"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CanvasGradient"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Creator methods in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a>.</li>\n  <li>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> element and its associated interface, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Instance properties","id":"instance_properties"},{"text":"Instance methods","id":"instance_methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The CanvasGradient interface represents an opaque object describing a gradient. It is returned by the methods CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient(), CanvasRenderingContext2D.createConicGradient() or CanvasRenderingContext2D.createRadialGradient().","popularity":0.0047,"modified":"2020-11-06T13:11:46.188Z","other_translations":[],"pageType":"web-api-interface","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/canvasgradient","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/canvasgradient/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/null","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"CanvasGradient","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient","title":"CanvasGradient"}],"pageTitle":"CanvasGradient - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false},"url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Can